{
  "stem": "8072.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, you do that one more time, you know-- we just kind of looked out for the underdog a little bit, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you just tried to survive, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It, it-- the work over there, the people where we did the work, they-- while you were working, the, the Germans, you know, that were in charge and things like that, they were more humane.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They weren't like, like you-- like you see some-- you work, and you didn't work fast enough, they come with a whip or something like that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a little more-- but I remember another thing, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "OK, now this was close to the war was ending.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When was that, then?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in, in April, March, April of, of '45.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were marching once to work, and they had already American planes throwing bombs in the area.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I know we were marching to work, and it was an open field.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, there comes the bombs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody's running, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans and everybody running in the bunkers and everything, like to hide.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a pile of hay or something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I just got up on the top of it, and started waving.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could've got shot for doing that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, I mean, that was the joy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't care if a bomb hit you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Did you see some bombs fall?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- we were-- it was a little bit away from camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, they didn't hit the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't hit the camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I was-- I, I I wished I-- they would throw more bombs, you know, to just clear it out, something like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
